data.name: Add to Announcement Temp
data.queryText:
select a.contactId, a.contactName, a.contactEmail, a.phoneNumber, 
a.title, a.name, a.announcementId, a.university, a.department, a.program, a.term, 
a.userGroup, a.startdate, a.endDate, a.createdDate, a.userId, a.uniqueId,a.departmentId,
announcementLink, bellTitle,body,recordtype


from
(select contactId, contactName, contactEmail, phoneNumber, Name, title,  announcementId, 
university, department, program, term, userGroup, startdate, endDate, createdDate, userId,uniqueId,
departmentId,announcementLink, bellTitle, body,recordtype,
ROW_NUMBER() over (partition by uniqueid
order by uniqueid) RowNumber  
from {{mcpm#/entities/dataExtensions/754d45b0-485c-ed11-ba55-f40343ce89d0/data/namePrefix}}[{{mcpm#/entities/dataExtensions/754d45b0-485c-ed11-ba55-f40343ce89d0/data/name}}]) a
where a.RowNumber = 1
and concat(a.announcementId, a.contactId, a.startDate,a.endDate) not IN (select  uniqueId from {{mcpm#/entities/dataExtensions/704d45b0-485c-ed11-ba55-f40343ce89d0/data/namePrefix}}[{{mcpm#/entities/dataExtensions/704d45b0-485c-ed11-ba55-f40343ce89d0/data/name}}])
